li><code>song</code>: the SoundCloud URL for your song: using\n<a href=\"http://github.com/hughsk/soundcloud-resolve\"><code>soundcloud-resolve</code></a>\nyou&apos;ll get the matching data for your song included.</li>\n<li><code>dark</code>: <code>true</code> for black text/icons, and <code>false</code> for white. Defaults to\n<code>true</code>.</li>\n<li><code>getFonts</code>: by default, the badge will pull in fonts from Google Fonts.\nSet this to <code>false</code> if you&apos;d rather it not do that.</li>\n</ul>\n"}